import { Image, Box, Text, Spacer } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

export default function FeatureIcon({ src, alt, link, heading, subheading }) {
  return (
    <Box p={4} display={{ md: "flex" }} alignItems="center">
      <Box flexShrink={0}>
        <Link to={link}>
          <Image src={src} alt={alt} borderRadius="xl" boxSize="150px" />
        </Link>
      </Box>
      <Spacer />
      <Box mt={{ base: 4, md: 0 }} ml={{ md: 6 }} textAlign="center">
        <Text
          fontWeight="bold"
          textTransform="uppercase"
          fontSize="sm"
          letterSpacing="wide"
          color="teal.600"
        >
          {heading}
        </Text>
        <Link
          mt={1}
          display="block"
          fontSize="lg"
          lineHeight="normal"
          fontWeight="semibold"
          href="#"
        >
          {subheading}
        </Link>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}
